### C
# Object files
*.o
*.obj
*.elf

# Precompiled Headers
*.gch
*.pch

# Libraries
*.lib
*.a
*.la
*.lo
*.dll
*.so
*.so.*
*.dylib

# Executables
*.exe
*.out

